tops.detail1: Cut to an oversized drop shouldered crew neck silhouette, the Fadu Sweater receives a collaborative update. The comfy sweater is made from 100% heavyweight cotton and features a branded graphic on the wearer’s chest. For an added detail, the sweater is finished off with a ribbed neck, cuffs and low-hanging waistband
tops.detail2: State-of-the-art dyeing techniques and classic sportswear silhouettes meet on this sweatshirt which is dyed using the innovative rain wash dying technique. Cut from a soft French terry cloth with ribbed cuffs and hem, this sweater was designed with comfort in mind. Cut with drop shoulders it has a contemporary oversized fit and features retro logo embroidery on the chest.
tops.detail3: Part of our second collaboration with the Van Gogh Museum, this t-shirt features a custom diptych graphic composed of the Dutch artist's 'Small Pear Tree in Blossom' and 'Baskets with Pansies'. Reproduced using a high-definition and ultra-bright rubber printing technique for maximum clarity and vibrancy. Constructed from a premium jersey and finished with our collaborative branding at the nape of the neck.
tops.detail4: A versatile wardrobe essential, our rendition of the basic t-shirt is now available in perfect pastel colourways. Crafted from premium heavyweight cotton with a loose ribbed collar, this tee has a high-quality look and feel without compromising on breathability and comfort. With a classic t-shirt shape and cut, it's guaranteed to be an indispensable layering piece.
tops.details5: State-of-the-art dyeing techniques and premium basics meet on this tee which is dyed using the innovative rain wash dying technique. Cut from a soft heavyweight cotton with a ribbed collar, this tee was designed with comfort in mind. Comes in a classic fit so size up for a more oversized silhouette. Dyed an eye-catching acid green and features retro logo embroidery on the chest

bottoms.detail1: With a unique allover comic book print, this jacket features the layout of the Comic Book created as part of the FW20 season. Washed for a softer on-skin feel, these straight legged 5-pocket jeans retain authentic details like donut buttons and rivet reinforcements. Best worn with matching Jarzeb Comic jacket for the full Comic Book look
bottoms.detail2: Part of our second collaboration with the Van Gogh Museum, these classic 5-pocket denim jeans feature one of the Dutch artist's floral compositions masterfully recreated on the front panels using state-of-the-art digital printing techniques. Cut from a rinse washed heavy denim in a cropped ankle length, these jeans are finished with a custom DP x VGM PU leather patch detail at the rear.
bottoms.detail3: The Cargo Pants are made in a classic Daily Paper pants silhouette and feature a comfortable fit. The pants are made out of fine soft cotton and have two front pockets and two back pockets for storing all your accessories.
bottoms.detail4: Designed in the classic silhouette, the Jiggy Sweatpants receives a collaborative update through a unique acid wash design. The comfy pants feature an elasticated waistband with an adjustable drawcord and two functional side pockets. The premium cotton is topped with a printed branded graphic on the wearer’s left thigh. Pair with the washed Fadu Sweater for the complete look.
bottoms.product_name5: Grey Lilac Teal Juka Pants 176.00 USD
bottoms.details5: A contemporary take on a classic trackpant featuring asymmetric panels of neutral greys, pastel lilac and teal overlaid on technical black nylon. This retro activewear is cut with a classic fit for unhindered movement and can be secured at the waist using a drawcord complete with metal branded lace tips. Pair this luxury track pant with the matching Jasah jacket for a retro-futuristic athletic sportswear aesthetic.

shoes.detail1: A modern classic, the Reslider Sandals are a must-have of any summer wardrobe. The moulded footbed provides optimal support and the premium padded strap guarantees comfort for everyday use. This easy to pair piece is finished with the reinvented new Daily Paper Shield Logo.

accessories.detail3: This contemporary headwear piece fuses a baseball cap with the aesthetics of a headscarf and features elongated panels at the side that hang down to the shoulders providing protection from bad weather. Constructed from a houndstooth fabric for a traditional tailoring spin on a sportswear classic.
accessories.detail4: This black quilted scarf with rectangular design fastens through the opening and provides extra warmth through the padded lining. The long style of the scarf allows you to wear it to your personal preference
accessories.details5: A classic fanny pack style bag reengineered as a shoulder bag. Crafted from a silky soft yet robust synthetic, the bag features two zipped pockets for easy hands-free storage and a metal logo in the front. A removable 'DAILY PAPER' branded strap allows the bag to be worn round the waist, under the shoulder or across the body for easy on-the-go adjustments to get a comfortable fit.
